{"type": "article", "id": 30217, "title": "H&M和Kenzo推出联名款，以及，Tom Ford的新电影来了｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-07-28T02:22:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 335, "name": "Uniqlo"}, {"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 976, "name": "Rihanna"}, {"id": 977, "name": "Tom Ford"}, {"id": 979, "name": "CFDA"}, {"id": 3472, "name": "周大福"}, {"id": 9418, "name": "Luxottica"}, {"id": 14244, "name": "浮华日报"}, {"id": 24892, "name": "Charlotte Tilbury"}, {"id": 30748, "name": "夜行动物"}, {"id": 30749, "name": "H&M 和 Kenzo"}, {"id": 30750, "name": "biketown"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160728074907OXkHDa03zZ7QwWcp.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/LVMH-fashion-and-leather-second-quarter-sales-beat-forecasts,717547.html#.V5f80GVuuT8\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>LVMH 最赚钱的时尚和皮具部门第二季度销售额上升 1% ，超预期</b></a>｜主要由美国市场，和亚洲市场（特别是日本）的需求拉动。<br></p><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-features/cfda-names-40-new-members-10495997/\" rel=\"nofollow\">美国时尚设计师协会增加 40 名新成员</a></b>｜至此成员总数达到 504 名。在 7 月 19 日举行的董事会上，还宣布了&nbsp;Diane von Furstenberg 将会一直出任协会主席到 2018 年。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-07-25/chow-tai-fook-plans-u-s-wholesale-business-amid-china-slowdown-ir2ku0vi\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>周大福在美国拓展批发业务，卖钻石给美国零售商</b></a>&nbsp;｜与周大福收购的珠宝品牌 Hearts on Fire 在美国售卖自家的珠宝不同，这个新业务将会售卖未经加工过的钻石。周大福表示对美国市场感兴趣，是因为美国是全球最大的钻石消费市场，占到了全球钻石销售的 40%。</p><p><a href=\"http://us.fashionmag.com/news/Luxottica-cuts-2016-outlook-as-U-S-weakness-hits-profit,717559.html#.V5lJL2VuuT8\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>意大利眼镜制造商 Luxottica 调低 2016 年销售预期&nbsp;</b></a>｜主要由于其全球最大市场北美市场的疲软，该市场占到总销售额的 60%。另外由于不安全因素也影响到了旅游消费。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.buro247.me/culture/films-and-theatre/tom-ford-set-to-premiere-film-during-2016-toronto.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Tom Ford 要在今年9 月多伦多国际电影节上首映他的新电影</b>&nbsp;</a>｜在 2009 年拍了《单身男子》之后，Tom Ford 的新电影《夜行动物》将会在 9 月多伦多国际电影节首映。影片由 Amy Adams 和 Jake Gyllenhaal 主演，剧本由 Tom Ford 根据 Austin Wright 在 1993 年出版的小说 Tony and Susan 改编而成。<br></p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/hm-previews-kenzo-collaboration-10496488/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>H&amp;M 和 Kenzo 推出联名款</b></a>，设计用到了不同颜色的虎纹元素，计划将在 11 月在其电商和全球精选的 250 家实体店售卖。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><span style=\"color: inherit; font-size: 18px; background-color: transparent;\"></span><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728073250laL16d7FiZAX8mgk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607280733107O3r9gi1hT406o2E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333984\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728073342NrqseoORFwzIJ7lK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://sneakernews.com/2016/07/13/nike-biketown-sneaker-bikes-air-max-95-air-safari-air-trainer-1/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Nike 发布了与波特兰交通局联手打造的 BIKETOWN 3 款公共自行车。</b></a>此前，曾公布过橙色自行车，这次公布的设计 Air Max 95、Air Trainer 1 和 Air Safari 为设计灵感。这 1000 辆公共自行车将会放在 100 个停车站，方便游客和当地居民出行。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607280818484lnNz8ZmAVo2Cy0Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665957\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728081859Q9SL6xghKiwJcEYI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665957\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728081904uMcNlKAU4B5EezHx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607280819151yvrRK56JMzNonAH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665957\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Charlotte Tilbury 推出第一款香水 Scent of a Dream，找来了 Kate Moss 代言。这款香水将在 8 月 15 日在其电商上开卖。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727190226aWgvTn2Y8QUyMNmj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">7 月 25 日&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.thefader.com/2016/07/26/rihanna-pop-up-shop-in-paris\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rihanna 在巴黎开了快闪店</a>。这个快闪电位于精品店&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.thefader.com/artist/colette\" sl-processed=\"1\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">Colette</a>&nbsp;，为期 5 天。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728073949g1eVFhomwcJTdbOv.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.855705\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607280739596BTV2WHZOMgaNybl.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.038298\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016072807400813abgVHFMIR6DELx.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.752961\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/accessories-news/footwear/jennifer-lopez-giuseppe-zanotti-shoes-collection-10496448/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jennifer&nbsp; Lopez 要和意大利设计师 Giuseppe Zanotti 联合推出鞋履和手袋。</a><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728080458KwlTz5iRXY3y19sg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562903\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">UNIQLO 秋季推出了经典的军事外套 MA-1 Flight Jacket。UNIQLO 的设计用到了尼龙材质，有黑色、军绿、海军蓝三种颜色。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160728082604XxqYfWvkZ8et7ol6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665644\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607280826181pGi0HlkOIobxNZ2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607280826425fyPEwWvIxZAlNjU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}